@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

autonumber

title Search Routes by Origin and Destination: Simplified Sequence Diagram

actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as S

ATCC -> S : Asks to search for routes
S --> ATCC : Requests origin airport, destination airport, or both
ATCC -> S : Types the search criteria
S -> S : Validates user permissions
S -> S : Checks if the provided airports exist
S -> S : Searches routes matching the criteria
S --> ATCC : Shows matching routes

@enduml